var socket = null;var sent = 0;var recv = 0;var length = 65536;function open(evt) {        message(evt);}function message(evt) {        socket.send(evt.data);        //sent = sent + 1;        update(evt);}function update(evt) {        filetable = document.getElementById("fileTable");        filetable.innerHTML = evt.data;}function onmessage(evt) {        message(evt);}function connect(url) {        //url file_index_connect        connect_url = "ws://127.0.0.1:8888/"+url        socket = new WebSocket(connect_url);        socket.onopen = function(evt) {                 if(url==="websocket_message_connect"){                        var filter  = document.getElementById("search").value;                        socket.send(filter);                } else {                        open(evt);                }                console.log("open");         };        socket.onclose = function(evt) {  console.log("closed");};        socket.onmessage = function(evt) {                 update(evt);                    //console.log(filter);                //console.log(message);                 socket.close();        };        socket.onerror = function(evt) { alert("onerror"); };}</script>
